pull.title: [qt] Remove excess logic: Prefer "return foo;" to "if (foo) { return true; } else { return false; }"
pull.body:
Replace …

```
if (foo) { return true; } else { return false; }
```

… with the equivalent …

```
return foo;
```

The code was introduced in fbf385cc830df2aec7cdcbab0c2b09b46569e8c1 which was merged into `master` earlier today.

Friendly ping @jonasschnelli :-)

events.body: Can you please add *somewhat* more description to your commit message and PR? Please don't just drop PRs without any description or motivation.
